        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
          <h2 style="font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--primary);margin:12px 0 20px;">Over Two Decades of Academic Excellence</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;">Founded in 2001 by a group of visionary educators and industry professionals, Himalayan Institute of Management &amp; Technology (HIMT) was established with a bold mission: to create a world-class educational institution in Nepal that bridges the gap between academic theory and industry practice.</p>
          <p style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:24px;">Starting with just two programs and 120 students in a modest campus in Lalitpur, HIMT has grown into one of Nepal's leading private colleges with over 2,500 enrolled students, 45 faculty members, and 5 academic departments — all affiliated to Tribhuvan University.</p>
          <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;">
            <div style="background:var(--light-bg);padding:20px;border-radius:var(--radius);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);">2001</div>
              <div style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-mid);">Year Established</div>
            </div>
            <div style="background:var(--light-bg);padding:20px;border-radius:var(--radius);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);">5000+</div>
