          <p style="color:var(--text-mid);font-size:0.92rem;line-height:1.8;">To provide quality, affordable, and accessible education in management and technology that empowers Nepali students to become skilled professionals and ethical leaders who contribute to national development and global progress.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="padding:36px;text-align:center;border-top:4px solid var(--accent);">
