          <p style="color:var(--text-mid);font-size:0.92rem;line-height:1.8;">To be the most respected educational institution in Nepal — recognized for academic rigor, research contributions, industry partnerships, and for shaping graduates who lead with integrity, competence, and compassion.</p>
