          <div style="width:90px;height:90px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--primary-light));border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:white;margin:0 auto 12px;">DK</div>
          <div style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);font-size:0.95rem;">Dr. Dipak Koirala</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;">Principal &amp; CEO</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.85;font-style:italic;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:16px;">"At HIMT, we believe education is not merely the transfer of knowledge — it is the transformation of character. Our goal has always been to develop graduates who are not only technically competent but also ethically grounded and socially responsible."</p>
          <p style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.85;font-size:0.9rem;">"Over the past 23 years, we have seen thousands of young Nepali students walk through our gates with dreams, and walk out with the skills and confidence to realize them. That remains our greatest achievement and our deepest motivation to continue improving every year."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

